Show HN: Writeathon – Connect your writing craft to final works
text:
Hi there,

I am a creative writing lover and prefer writing in odd moment e.g., taking the subway, having coffee and so on. There are lots of pieces from the odd moment writing need to be arranged and combined to the final pages. Then I made the Writeathon to help me.

Key Features:

- Slip Box: Help you write craft in card, anywhere, anytime. (A handy app provided) - Card Writing Mode: Help you arrange and combine the craft cards to the final pages. - Writing: Help you write in immersion with Zen Mode, Flow Mode, and White Noises.

One More Thing: - Writeathon Live: Help you create live writing marathon to write together in group, with custom writing goal, topic.

Alternative: - Scrivener - Evernote - Google keeps.

Just go to writeathon.app to get the full features or writeathon.app/app to download the iOS or Android app. Any feedback is welcome from you.

Thanks!
